## Product [/products/{productId}]
A single Product object with all its details

+ Parameters
    + productId (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `productId` of the Product to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Product [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            ETag: "e3e824c6-6358-4dcf-b16b-03555004a8c1"

    + Body

