# Group Cart
Shopping Cart related resources of the **Shop API**

## Shopping Cart [/cart]
### Add a Product to Cart [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        { "productId": 123 }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        { "cartId": 1, "productId": 123 }

## Cart Item [/cart/{cartId}]
A single Cart item.

+ Parameters
    + cartId (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `cartId` of the Product to perform action with. Has example value.
    
### Remove a Product from Cart [DELETE]
+ Response 204
